* {{Persian/text|نیست|nist| he/she/it is not}}, colloquially pronounced ‹nis›
* {{Persian/text|نیستیم|nistim| we are not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیستید|nistid|you are not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیستند|nistand|they are not}}, colloquially pronounced ‹nistan›

